    },
    {
      "block_id": "669760b2-8179-4d2e-a071-09e15c632b8c",
      "text": "1. AUTOMATION CLAIMS",
      "source_type": "policy_document",
      "frame_index": null,
      "timestamp": null,
      "page_number": 2,
      "document_path": "/Users/padlet/instalily/data/sample_policies/sample_policy.txt",
      "bounding_box": null,
      "confidence": 1.0,
      "model_used": "text-parser"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "9135e583-7e66-4fb1-8f03-b486e27ece40",
      "text": "1.1 Products or features described as \"automated\" must include a disclosure\n    when manual review or human oversight is required in any operational path.",
      "source_type": "policy_document",
      "frame_index": null,
      "timestamp": null,
      "page_number": 3,
      "document_path": "/Users/padlet/instalily/data/sample_policies/sample_policy.txt",
      "bounding_box": null,
      "confidence": 1.0,
      "model_used": "text-parser"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "8060b816-18eb-4f29-9157-e5d6db282ea7",
      "text": "1.2 The phrase \"fully automated\" is prohibited unless the product processes\n    100% of cases without human intervention, as verified by QA sign-off.",
      "source_type": "policy_document",
      "frame_index": null,
      "timestamp": null,
      "page_number": 4,
      "document_path": "/Users/padlet/instalily/data/sample_policies/sample_policy.txt",
      "bounding_box": null,
      "confidence": 1.0,
      "model_used": "text-parser"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "65a1ad6b-3bf3-488d-91a5-f9abccfae187",
      "text": "1.3 Acceptable alternative: \"automated for standard cases; edge cases are\n    reviewed by our compliance team within 24 hours.\"",
      "source_type": "policy_document",
      "frame_index": null,
      "timestamp": null,
      "page_number": 5,
      "document_path": "/Users/padlet/instalily/data/sample_policies/sample_policy.txt",
      "bounding_box": null,
      "confidence": 1.0,
      "model_used": "text-parser"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "7a144ebf-93d5-400a-98de-36b6c10665f2",
      "text": "2. APPROVAL AND PROCESSING TIME",
      "source_type": "policy_document",
      "frame_index": null,
      "timestamp": null,
      "page_number": 6,
      "document_path": "/Users/padlet/instalily/data/sample_policies/sample_policy.txt",
      "bounding_box": null,
      "confidence": 1.0,
      "model_used": "text-parser"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "1f34a732-430d-4a41-bd8c-929f42fb9f28",
      "text": "2.1 Claims of \"instant approval\" must be qualified with the expected time\n    range (e.g., \"typically within seconds for standard submissions\").",
      "source_type": "policy_document",
      "frame_index": null,
      "timestamp": null,
      "page_number": 7,
      "document_path": "/Users/padlet/instalily/data/sample_policies/sample_policy.txt",
      "bounding_box": null,
      "confidence": 1.0,
      "model_used": "text-parser"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "4452672f-f54a-42c8-8780-c53059aa2149",
      "text": "2.2 \"Zero manual steps\" claims are only permissible for products that have\n    achieved Tier-1 automation certification from the Product Operations team.",
      "source_type": "policy_document",
      "frame_index": null,
      "timestamp": null,
      "page_number": 8,
      "document_path": "/Users/padlet/instalily/data/sample_policies/sample_policy.txt",
      "bounding_box": null,
      "confidence": 1.0,
      "model_used": "text-parser"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "88c444fd-c73d-4467-9ac4-d5a99080abf4",
      "text": "2.3 For uncertified products, use: \"minimal manual intervention required.\"",
      "source_type": "policy_document",
      "frame_index": null,
      "timestamp": null,
      "page_number": 9,
      "document_path": "/Users/padlet/instalily/data/sample_policies/sample_policy.txt",
      "bounding_box": null,
      "confidence": 1.0,
      "model_used": "text-parser"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "95973914-abc1-476d-a9a7-fe17b3f24eb8",
      "text": "3. ACCURACY AND PERFORMANCE METRICS",
      "source_type": "policy_document",
      "frame_index": null,
      "timestamp": null,
      "page_number": 10,
      "document_path": "/Users/padlet/instalily/data/sample_policies/sample_policy.txt",
      "bounding_box": null,
      "confidence": 1.0,
      "model_used": "text-parser"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "522daba3-0ca7-4f8d-a0de-0c600699de0a",
      "text": "3.1 All accuracy figures used in sales or marketing materials must be\n    sourced from a published internal benchmark report, referenced by ID.",
      "source_type": "policy_document",
      "frame_index": null,
      "timestamp": null,
      "page_number": 11,
      "document_path": "/Users/padlet/instalily/data/sample_policies/sample_policy.txt",
      "bounding_box": null,
      "confidence": 1.0,
      "model_used": "text-parser"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "6a8f9e15-c7f4-4159-9074-925c2b21007b",
      "text": "3.2 Claims of \"99%\" or higher accuracy require executive sign-off and must\n    include the test dataset description and date.",
      "source_type": "policy_document",
      "frame_index": null,
      "timestamp": null,
      "page_number": 12,
      "document_path": "/Users/padlet/instalily/data/sample_policies/sample_policy.txt",
      "bounding_box": null,
      "confidence": 1.0,
      "model_used": "text-parser"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "13a44789-35aa-4e57-bad5-5ba27406c679",
      "text": "3.3 Contextualise accuracy: state the task, dataset size, and timeframe.",
      "source_type": "policy_document",
      "frame_index": null,
      "timestamp": null,
      "page_number": 13,
      "document_path": "/Users/padlet/instalily/data/sample_policies/sample_policy.txt",
      "bounding_box": null,
      "confidence": 1.0,
      "model_used": "text-parser"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "91fae32d-da95-47e6-8097-a4038e009b34",
      "text": "4. PRIVACY AND DATA HANDLING",
      "source_type": "policy_document",
      "frame_index": null,
      "timestamp": null,
      "page_number": 14,
      "document_path": "/Users/padlet/instalily/data/sample_policies/sample_policy.txt",
      "bounding_box": null,
      "confidence": 1.0,
      "model_used": "text-parser"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "8d47df36-f0c6-4b8c-9913-37b5bf3481e4",
      "text": "4.1 \"On-device\" or \"private by design\" claims are valid only if the product\n    processes all data locally without transmitting customer data externally.",
      "source_type": "policy_document",
      "frame_index": null,
      "timestamp": null,
      "page_number": 15,
      "document_path": "/Users/padlet/instalily/data/sample_policies/sample_policy.txt",
      "bounding_box": null,
      "confidence": 1.0,
      "model_used": "text-parser"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "4e963df3-c7d0-44c3-b92e-cde241cc6f61",
      "text": "4.2 If any optional cloud functionality exists (even as a fallback), the\n    privacy claim must be qualified: \"on-device by default; cloud features\n    are opt-in and clearly disclosed.\"",
      "source_type": "policy_document",
      "frame_index": null,
      "timestamp": null,
      "page_number": 16,
      "document_path": "/Users/padlet/instalily/data/sample_policies/sample_policy.txt",
      "bounding_box": null,
      "confidence": 1.0,
      "model_used": "text-parser"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "f927695e-c43a-4d9a-84fc-0c26aa8f8cd8",
      "text": "4.3 \"Data never leaves the device\" is a strong claim requiring legal review\n    before use in customer-facing materials.",
      "source_type": "policy_document",
      "frame_index": null,
      "timestamp": null,
      "page_number": 17,
      "document_path": "/Users/padlet/instalily/data/sample_policies/sample_policy.txt",
      "bounding_box": null,
      "confidence": 1.0,
      "model_used": "text-parser"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "36f65429-f559-4d86-9da6-6c1a21f3c34f",
      "text": "5. COMPARISON CLAIMS",
      "source_type": "policy_document",
      "frame_index": null,
      "timestamp": null,
      "page_number": 18,
      "document_path": "/Users/padlet/instalily/data/sample_policies/sample_policy.txt",
      "bounding_box": null,
      "confidence": 1.0,
      "model_used": "text-parser"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "df20b0c5-7353-4e31-87cc-084bbb60da07",
      "text": "5.1 Comparative claims (e.g., \"faster than X\", \"more accurate than Y\") must\n    reference a specific, dated benchmark and be approved by Product Marketing.",
      "source_type": "policy_document",
      "frame_index": null,
      "timestamp": null,
      "page_number": 19,
      "document_path": "/Users/padlet/instalily/data/sample_policies/sample_policy.txt",
      "bounding_box": null,
      "confidence": 1.0,
      "model_used": "text-parser"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b55647ed-cc79-475d-9296-00cfd65ebea3",
      "text": "5.2 Unnamed competitor comparisons (\"unlike other solutions\") are permitted\n    only if the comparison is verifiable by an independent third party.",
      "source_type": "policy_document",
      "frame_index": null,
      "timestamp": null,
      "page_number": 20,
      "document_path": "/Users/padlet/instalily/data/sample_policies/sample_policy.txt",
      "bounding_box": null,
      "confidence": 1.0,
      "model_used": "text-parser"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "af707c17-223f-4a1d-b3e2-4d3c79456c77",
      "text": "6. FINANCIAL PROJECTIONS",
      "source_type": "policy_document",
      "frame_index": null,
      "timestamp": null,
      "page_number": 21,
      "document_path": "/Users/padlet/instalily/data/sample_policies/sample_policy.txt",
      "bounding_box": null,
      "confidence": 1.0,
